# ARES-NAV Development Roadmap

This roadmap describes the public development phases of the ARES-NAV project.

## Phase 1 — Concept Development

* Navigation architecture research
* System concept definition
* Interface design exploration

## Phase 2 — Experimental Platform

* Prototype development
* Sensor interface research
* Visualization systems

## Phase 3 — Integrated Navigation Research

* Robust state estimation exploration
* System health monitoring
* fault detection research

## Phase 4 — Interface and Visualization

* Advanced flight display design
* User interface refinement
* system visualization tools

## Phase 5 — Extended Research

* advanced navigation studies
* resilience testing
* experimental avionics development
